headline: Shield AI and L3Harris Team for Breakthrough in Autonomy
summary: Shield AI and L3Harris Technologies [NYSE: LHX] will collaborate on a demonstration to enable an electronic warfare (EW) operation with AI-enabled unmanned systems that will sense, adapt and act while simultaneously executing physical and electromagnetic movements.
